Package mms.mediaworker

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MediaPlayer
    Class implementing the media player using Xuggler Library to encoding video file and a JFrame VideoFrame to display the video file.
    VideoFilter
    Class implementing different FileFilter for JFileChooser.
    VideoFrame
    This class just displays a 2d graphic on a Swing window.
    VideoIcon
    Class used to add an ImageIcon to a file video.
    VideoResizer
    Class used to resize a video file.
